TI  - On-Board Support System for the eco-friendly ship operation in coastal and port areas
PY  - 2019
T2  - OCEANS 2019 - Marseille, OCEANS Marseille 2019
VL  - 2019-June
C7  - 8867157
DO  - 10.1109/OCEANSE.2019.8867157
